95
00:04:12.420 --> 00:04:16.239
like data encoding feature mapping in error mitigation

96
00:04:16.240 --> 00:04:18.860
in some cases these differences between classical

97
00:04:18.860 --> 00:04:21.440
and quantum computers allow us to design entirely

98
00:04:21.440 --> 00:04:25.340
